gmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係自己跌左<br />\n由酒店出發到換錢個程路 應該冇機會俾人偷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46dd4167dcb0ab9529bfb3cb8585f3dcba451c5","tid":130543,"uid":9558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港紙五千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臨走執野先發現<br />\n應該比hostel 啲仆街偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 好明你心情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後有冇攞返？</blockquote><br />\n無，都過左幾年，當破財擋災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eebc9ec1f6f15953e24a15345367edce95e3a69","tid":130543,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跌定比人偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當破財擋災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係自己跌左<br />\n由酒店出發到換錢個程路 應該冇機會俾人偷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗱，唔見錢你就一定要報警咖喇。不過冇拉拉鍊，定拉鍊比人打開，就兩回事黎嘅。<br />\n<br />\n冇拉拉鍊就你自己問題冇得賠，人地拉開左就係比人偷有得賠。<br />\n<br />\n我上次去九份，個拉鍊就比人拉開左拎左裏面嘅錢，賠左3000蚊。<br />\n<br />\n只要你係確認你酒店離開個時有關好，到目的地發現開左，基本上都已經可以界定比人偷野"}]}